**Describe the bug**
Trying to do a zoom of document.

**To Reproduce**
Settings settings = new Settings();
DocumentSettingsPart docSetPart = mainPart.AddNewPart<DocumentSettingsPart>();

XZoom zoom = new XZoom() { Percent = "200" };
settings.Zoom = zoom;
HideSpellingErrors hideSpellingErrors = new HideSpellingErrors();
settings.HideSpellingErrors = hideSpellingErrors;

docSetPart.Settings = settings;
// also added som test texts and generated a dokument.

**Observed behavior**
No zoom when open document, but "settings.HideSpellingErrors" working as expected.

**Expected behavior**
Zoom.

**Desktop (please complete the following information):**
    OS: Windows 11
    Office version Microsoft® Word 2021 MSO (Version 2308 Build 16.0.16731.20182) 64-bitars
    .NET Target: .NET 6.0
    Windows Forms project
    Visual Studio 2022 ver 17.7.3
    DocumentFormat.OpenXml Version: 2.20.0

